应用介绍：
校体云（青少年体质健康管理系统）——为中小学生提供体质健康的监测、检测、采集、数据分析、数据平台、运动处方、体育课改等一系列学校体育信息化与学生体质健康整体解决方案。

【产品特点】
@提升学生体质健康，专家团队专业分析
@体测体质 语系转换丨发现孩子体质弱项，针对性改善
@定制化 改善方案丨让每个学生都有自己的运动“私教”
@个性化 健康食谱丨绘制孩子专属生长曲线，专业有营养
@AI科技 体感运动丨 精准动作识别 实时智能纠错

一句话简介：校体云----青少年体质健康管理系统

1. Knowledge in Life：
- Ten daily life topics include: Transportation, Animals, Nature, Community, Health and Hygiene, School, Go Green, Food, Self and Family, People who help us;
- Children have access to diverse topics according to their interests and age;
- Provides activities, worksheets and project exploration.


2. School-Based Curriculum：
- Exclusive for School Users;
- A Multi-media Learning Platform for schools;
- Easy for schools to organise learning topics;
- Allows parents and children to review learning progress in school.


3. Origin of Chinese characters：
- Selects 52 of the most frequently-used characters in kindergarten;
- Introduces strokes, pronunciation and the evolution of characters with fun animations;
- Provides word-matching games.


4. Festival：
- Different animated stories including Christmas, Lunar New Year and Mid-Autumn Festival etc.;
- Allows children to gain better understanding of different festivals.


5. Language (Chinese)：
- Handpicks 90 animated stories about the language according to ten daily life topic for K1-K3 children;
- Introduces new words and sentence structures;
- Enhances children’s language ability.


6. Explore 360:
- New animations updated every week;
- Provides Cantonese, Putonghua and English versions;
- Contents are fun, informative and engaging;
- Includes topics related to children’s daily lives and moral education.


